<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Proje Envanter - TÜBİTAK Sunumu</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Urbanist:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-bg: #0f172a;
            --accent-green: #10b981;
            --text-light: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
            --border-color: #334155;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            display: grid;
            gap: 20px;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            place-items: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            font-family: 'Urbanist', sans-serif;
        }

        .slide-container {
            width: 1280px;
            height: 720px;
            background-color: var(--primary-bg);
            color: var(--text-light);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 60px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .slide-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -10%;
            right: -10%;
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .slide-container::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 30px;
            right: 30px;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--border-color);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .slide-title {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: var(--text-light);
            border-left: 6px solid var(--accent-green);
            padding-left: 20px;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        .slide-title span {
            color: var(--accent-green);
        }

        p, li {
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .content-area {
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .title-layout {
            text-align: center;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .title-layout h1 {
            font-size: 82px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .title-layout .subtitle {
            font-size: 28px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .two-column {
            display: flex;
            gap: 50px;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .col { flex: 1; }

        .image-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .image-wrapper img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .tiled-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .tile {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .tile i {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: var(--accent-green);
        }

        .tile h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .tile p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        th {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            text-align: left;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-green);
        }

        td {
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .chart-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .bar-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .bar-label { width: 250px; text-align: right; }

        .bar-bg {
            flex-grow: 1;
            height: 30px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .bar-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-green), #34d399);
            border-radius: 15px;
        }

        .timeline {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            position: relative;
            padding-top: 40px;
        }

        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--border-color);
        }

        .timeline-step {
            width: 20%;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .timeline-dot {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: var(--accent-green);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .bleed-image-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            padding: 0;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .bleed-image-layout .text-side {
            padding: 60px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 720px;
        }

        .bleed-image-layout img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 720px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .bullet-list {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .bullet-list li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 35px;
        }

        .bullet-list li::before {
            content: '→';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--accent-green);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer-note {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 15px;
            right: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- SLIDE 1: KAPAK -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide1">
    <div class="title-layout content-area">
        <h1>PROJE <span>ENVANTER</span></h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Tedarik Zinciri Dayanıklılığı ve İthal İkamesi İçin Milli B2B Satın Alma Ekosistemi.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 40px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent-green);">Stratejik Hizalanma: Türkiye Yüzyılı (2024-2028)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-note">GİZLİ | TÜBİTAK 1812 PROJE ÖNERİSİ</div>
</div>

<!-- SLIDE 2: PROBLEM -->
